Package: reefCloudPackage
Type: Package
Title: ReefCloud Statistical Modelling Package
Version: 0.1.2
Author: Murray Logan, Julie Vercelloni
Maintainer: Murray Logan <murray.logan@aims.gov.au>
Description: Statistical modelling and analysis tools for coral reef monitoring data.
    Provides functions for data loading, processing, spatial-temporal modelling,
    and visualization of reef health metrics across different spatial tiers.
